    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，五个section：Discovery（发现）、Onboarding（引导）、Gameplay（核心玩法）、Victory/Defeat（结果反馈）、Engagement（持续参与）。每个环节都要标注玩家和系统的满意度评分，1-5分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Discovery",
        "Onboarding",
        "Gameplay",
